          <li class="red">Poor nutrition</li>
          <li class="red">Direct/continuous exposure to light source or/and ultraviolet radiation</li>
          <li class="red">Aging</li>
          <li class="red">Spending several hours routinely reading, watching televisions, computers and similar electronic
            gadgets</li>
          <li class="red">Other medical conditions (like hypertention, diabetes mellitus and heart diseases)</li>
  
