          <li>You can wear a hat in addition to above to create added protection when outdoors</li>
          <li class="blue">Regular (yearly) routine general medical screening</li>
          <li class="blue">Report illness early to authorized medical facilities</li>
          <li class="blue">Avoid alcohol as much as possible</li>
          <li class="blue">Avoid smoking and smoking environment</li>
          <li class="blue">At least 30minutes of exercise(like walking) per day</li>
          <li class="blue">Delibrate efforts at eating locally available nutritious and healthy foods</li>
